    <detaileddescription>
<para>Tests the behavior of NV097_SET_POINT_SIZE and NV097_SET_POINT_SMOOTH_ENABLE</para>
<para>See <ulink url="https://registry.khronos.org/OpenGL-Refpages/gl2.1/xhtml/glPointSize.xml">https://registry.khronos.org/OpenGL-Refpages/gl2.1/xhtml/glPointSize.xml</ulink></para>
<para>Each test renders a grid of points.</para>
<para>As points go from left to right: point size starts at 0 and increases by point_size_increment per point. </para>
